Reinsurance Claims Officer
Emirates Retakaful Limited
Dubai, UAE
Posted on: 2 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
You must have:
•Experience in day to day management of Reinsurance claims – Treaty and Facultative.
•Knowledge of Reinsurance and its concept’s.
•Process claim advices and system entry.
•Execute all assignments delegated well within the time frame.
•Must be pro active & self motivated.
•Should be a good team player.
REQUIREMENTS
Qualifications:
•Three to Four years of experience in Reinsurance (Non Life Only – Property, Engineering, Marine & General Accident).
•Any Graduate from a reputed institution and Insurance related certificate is an added advantage.
•Fluent in English.
•Knowledge of Arabic will be an added advantage.
•Good knowledge of Microsoft office and confidence with systems.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
EmiratesRE The first leading Retakaful Institution for regional and worldwide markets, grounded on Fiqh Al Muamalat, observing the rules and regulations of the Islamic society.
Emirates Re is committed to enriching the Retakaful and Insurance industries in accordance with Shari’a principles by providing first-class levels of expertise, products and services. We transact several lines of business on a Treaty and Facultative basis:
• Property
• Engineering
• Marine
• Accident
• Motor
• Energy
